#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introdución"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kturtle; is an educational programming environment that uses <link linkend="
"\"what-is-turtlelang\">&turtlescript;</link>, a programming language loosely "
"based on and inspired by &logo;. The goal of &kturtle; is to make "
"programming as easy and accessible as possible. This makes &kturtle; "
"suitable for teaching kids the basics of math, geometry and... programming. "
"One of the main features of &turtlescript; is the ability to translate the "
"commands into the speaking language of the programmer."
msgstr ""
"&kturtle; é un ambiente de programación para a educación que usa <link "
"linkend=\"what-is-turtlelang\">&turtlescript;</link>, unha linguaxe de "
"programación inspirada en &logo; e baseada nesta. O propósito de &kturtle; é "
"simplificar a programación e facela tan accesíbel como for posíbel. Isto fai "
"que &kturtle; sexa axeitado para ensinarlles aos cativos os fundamentos das "
"matemáticas, a xeometría e a programación. Unha das principais "
"características de &turtlescript; é que as ordes da linguaxe poden "
"traducirse ao idioma do programador."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kturtle; is named after <quote>the turtle</quote> that plays a central role "
"in the programming environment. The student will usually instruct the "
"turtle, using the &turtlescript; commands, to make a drawing on <link "
"linkend=\"the-canvas\">the canvas</link>."
msgstr ""
"O nome de &kturtle; procede <quote>do sapoconcho</quote> que ten un papel "
"central no ambiente de programación. O estudante normalmente ordenaralle ao "
"sapoconcho, mediante as ordes de &turtlescript;, que debuxe unha imaxe no "
"<link linkend=\"the-canvas\">lenzo</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is &turtlescript;?"
msgstr "Que é &turtlescript;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&turtlescript;, the programming language used in &kturtle;, is inspired "
#| "by the &logo; family of programming languages. The first version of "
#| "&logo; was created by Seymour Papert of MIT Artificial Intelligence "
#| "Laboratory in 1967 as an offshoot of the LISP programming language. From "
#| "then many versions of &logo; have been released. By 1980 &logo; was "
#| "gaining momentum, with versions for MSX, Commodore, Atari, Apple II and "
#| "IBM PC systems. These versions were mainly for educational purposes. The "
#| "MIT is still maintains <ulink url=\"http://el.media.mit.edu/logo-"
#| "foundation/\">a website on &logo;</ulink> containing a list of several "
#| "popular implementation of the language."
msgid ""
"&turtlescript;, the programming language used in &kturtle;, is inspired by "
"the &logo; family of programming languages. The first version of &logo; was "
"created by Seymour Papert of MIT Artificial Intelligence Laboratory in 1967 "
"as an offshoot of the LISP programming language. From then many versions of "
"&logo; have been released. By 1980 &logo; was gaining momentum, with "
"versions for MSX, Commodore, Atari, Apple II and IBM PC systems. These "
"versions were mainly for educational purposes. The MIT is still maintains "
"<ulink url=\"https://el.media.mit.edu/logo-foundation/\">a website on &logo;"
"</ulink> containing a list of several popular implementation of the language."
msgstr ""
"&turtlescript;, a linguaxe de programación empregada en &kturtle;, está "
"inspirada na familia de linguaxes de programación &logo;. A primeira versión "
"de &logo; creouna Seymour Papert do Laboratorio de Intelixencia Artificial "
"do MIT en 1967 como fillo da linguaxe LISP. Desde entón publicáronse varias "
"versións de &logo;. En 1980 &logo; gañou popularidade: había versións para "
"MSX, Commodore, Atari, Apple II e IBM PC. Estas versións foron "
"principalmente destinadas a usos educativos. O MIT aínda mantén <ulink url="
"\"http://el.media.mit.edu/logo-foundation/\">ten un sitio web sobre &logo;</"
"ulink> que contén unha lista de varias realizacións populares desta linguaxe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&turtlescript; shares a feature found in many other implementations of "
"&logo;: the ability to translate the commands to suit the native language of "
"the student. This feature makes it easier for students that have no or "
"little understanding of English to get started. Besides this feature "
"&kturtle; has <link linkend=\"features-of-kturtle\">many other features</"
"link> aimed at easing the students initial experience with programming."
msgstr ""
"&turtlescript; comparte unha funcionalidade que se atopa en moitas outras "
"realizacións de &logo;: a posibilidade de traducir as ordes ao idioma nativo "
"do estudante. Isto fai máis sinxelo comezar para os estudantes que non "
"coñecen ou que coñecen moi pouco inglés. Ademais desta característica "
"&kturtle; ten <link linkend=\"features-of-kturtle\">moitas outras</link> que "
"intentan simplificar as primeiras experiencias dos estudantes coa "
"programación."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features of &kturtle;"
msgstr "Funcionalidades de &kturtle;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kturtle; has some nice features that make starting to program a breeze. See "
"here some of the highlights of &kturtle; feature set:"
msgstr ""
"&kturtle; ten algunhas características que facilitan moito o comezar a "
"programar. Estas son algunhas das funcionalidades máis realzábeis de "
"&kturtle;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An integrated environment with &turtlescript; interpreter, <link linkend="
"\"the-editor\">editor</link>, <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">canvas</link> and "
"other tools all in one application (no extra dependencies)."
msgstr ""
"Un ambiente integrado cun intérprete de &turtlescript;, <link linkend=\"the-"
"editor\">editor</link>, <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">lenzo</link> e outras "
"utilidades todas xuntas nun aplicativo (sen dependencias adicionais)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ability to translate the &turtlescript; commands using the translation "
"framework of &kde;."
msgstr ""
"A posibilidade de traducir as ordes de &turtlescript; usando a "
"infraestrutura de tradución de &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&turtlescript; supports user defined functions, recursion and dynamic type "
"switching."
msgstr ""
"&turtlescript; permítelle o usuario definir funcións, recursión e cambio "
"dinámico de tipos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "The execution can be slowed down, paused or stopped at any time."
msgstr ""
"A execución pode ralentizarse, pausarse ou deterse en calquera momento."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A powerful <link linkend=\"the-editor\">editor</link> featuring intuitive "
"syntax highlighting, line numbering, error markers, visual execution and "
"more."
msgstr ""
"Un potente <link linkend=\"the-editor\">editor</link> con realzado intuitivo "
"da sintaxe, numeración de liñas, marcas de erros, execución visual e máis "
"cousas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">canvas</link>, where the turtle draws, "
#| "can be printed or saved either as an image (PNG) or a drawing (SVG)."
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">canvas</link>, where the turtle draws, can "
"be printed or saved either as an image (PNG) or a drawing (&SVG;)."
msgstr ""
"O <link linkend=\"the-canvas\">lenzo</link>, onde debuxa o sapoconcho, pode "
"imprimirse ou gardarse como unha imaxe (PNG) ou debuxo (SVG)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Context help: help where you need it. Just press <keysym>F2</keysym> (or see "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Help on: ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>) to get help on the piece of code currently under your cursor."
msgstr ""
"Axuda contextual: onde a precise. Prema <keysym>F2</keysym> (ou consulte "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Axuda</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sobre: …</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>) para obter axuda sobre a peza de código que teña baixo o cursor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An error dialog that links the error messages to the mistakes in the program "
"and marks them red."
msgstr ""
"Un diálogo de erro que liga as mensaxes de erro cos erros no programa e que "
"as sinala en vermello."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simplified programming terminology."
msgstr "Terminoloxía de programación moi simplificada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Integrated example programs to make it easy to get started. These examples "
"are translated using &kde; translation framework."
msgstr ""
"Programas de exemplo para facilitar aínda máis os inicios. Estes exemplo "
"tradúcense usando a infraestrutura de tradución de &kde;."

